prodNameC: 速樂定胎兒蛋白檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
B：Serum Diluent(Liquid)
Phosphate buffer saline containing normal rabbit sera and 0.1% sodium azide.
C：Antibody-Sensitized Cells(Lyophilized)
Lyophilized preparation of fixed chicken erythrocytes sensitized with anti-AFP mouse antibody. The reconstituted reagent includes 0.66% anti-AFP Antibody-Sensitized Cells.
D：Control Cells(Lyophilized)
Lyophilized preparation of fixed chicken erythrocytes sensitized with mouse IgG.
E：Positive Control(Liquid)
1：10 diluted preparation of human serum positive for AFP with Serum Diluent. The control include gives a 1：320 end point titer at final dilution when tested according to the Positive Control Test Procedure
F：Absorbent Cells (Lyophilized)
Lyophilized preparation of chicken erythrocytes sensitized with mouse IgG..
